🧑‍💻 What is the job of a Site Reliability Engineer (SRE)?
A Site Reliability Engineer ensures that services are:

Highly available

Performant

Scalable

Monitored and reliable

SREs bridge the gap between software development and IT operations using automation, monitoring, incident response, and performance tuning.



🧠 In Short: As an SRE, your work in Prometheus & Grafana includes:
Setting up monitoring

Writing metrics & alert rules

Creating dashboards

Handling alerts and incidents

Automating health checks and ensuring SLA/SLO compliance
